name: Transferred to 1.1.1.348 and 4.2.1.139
classes: Acting on the CH-OH group of donors;
With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
comment: Transferred entry: pterocarpin synthase. This activity is now known to be catalysed by two enzymes, vestitone reductase (EC 1.1.1.348) and medicarpin synthase (EC 4.2.1.139).
